rule-4-1-a.test_description: Baseline and Proposed building have one building segment and  one zone with matching thermostat schedules. Expected result: PASS

standard.rule_description: Temperature Control Setpoints shall be the same for proposed design and baseline building design.

rule-4-1-b.test_description: Baseline and Proposed building have one building segment and  one zone with non-matching thermostat schedules. Expected result: UNDETERMINED

standard.rule_description: Temperature Control Setpoints shall be the same for proposed design and baseline building design.
